'''Onesmus Kimweli Mutungi''' (1940–2016) was a [[Kenyan]] judge and law professor. He was the first Kenyan ever to get a doctoral degree in law. He was also the first dean of the [[University of Nairobi]] School of Law.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nation.co.ke/news/Law-Professor-Onesmus-Mutungi-passes-on/1056-3413004-2k38eoz/index.html|title=Law Professor Onesmus Mutungi passes on|publisher=www.nation.co.ke}}</ref>
